      "title": "COVID-19: Five more deaths, 181 new cases reported",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Five more Covid-19 deaths that occurred yesterday(12) were confirmed by the Director General of Health Services today increasing the Civid-19 death toll in Sri Lanka to 16, 954.",
        "Meanwhile, 181 fresh Covid-19 patients were identified today, increasing the total number of Covid patients in Sri Lanka to 667, 916."
